use spacetimedb::table;

#[table(name = users)]
pub struct User {
    #[primary_key]
    id: i32,
    name: String,
    age: i32,
    active: bool,
}

#[table(name = products)]
pub struct Product {
    #[primary_key]
    id: i32,
    title: String,
    price: f32,
    in_stock: bool,
}

#[table(name = notes)]
pub struct Note {
    #[primary_key]
    id: i32,
    body: String,
    rating: i64,
    pinned: bool,
}

}
